						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying near the image of Āñjaneya.</p>						

						<p>Kākatīya Pratāparudra, A.D. 1313.</p>						

						<p>Dated Śaka 1235, <hi rend="italic">Pramādīcha, Kārtīka,</hi> śu. 15, Thursday, corresponding to A.D. 1313, November. 3.</p>						

						<p>Seems to record a gift of land for a garden to the god Tripurantaka Mahadeva by Mallaṇadevaṇṇa with the permission of Potaya-sāhiṇi.</p>						

						</summary>
