<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>Figures of Cresent moon and sun.</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śakavarṣaṁbulu 1235 Agunēṭi 
<lb n="2"/>pramādīca saṁvatsara kārtīka śu 15 gu svasti śrīmanma<unclear>hāma</unclear> 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁḍalēśvara kākatiyya pratāpa rudradēva mahārājula ja <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/><unclear>pōta</unclear>yasāhiṇigāri Ānatini mallaṇadēvaṇnaṁgāru 
<lb n="5"/><unclear>tannēlina svāmi</unclear> pratāparudradēva mahārājulakāyu 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rārōgyaiśvaryyābhivṛddhigānu tripurāṁttakamulōnu 
<lb n="7"/>tripurāṁtka(taka) śrīmanmahādēvarakuṁ buvuṁdōṁ 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṭa peṭṭiṁcci Ātōṁṭapaṭṭuna darasi polānanu Ū 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ri dakṣiṇānanu mōṭirēgaṭanu kha 3 na 16 podukamūri 
<lb n="10"/>teruvu Uttarānanu kha 1 na <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> Aṭuverasi kha 5 I 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ccenu vrittigānu ĀcaṁdrārkasthāI(yi)gānu Icci 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ri paṁggamulēdu sarvvamānyamu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
<lb n="13"/>svadattā dviguṇaṁ puṇyaṁ paradattānupālanaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
<lb n="14"/><unclear>paradattāpahārēṇa</unclear> svadattaṁ niṣphalaṁ bhavēt <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
<lb n="15"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
</p>

